source.name: Capital District Transportation Authority (CDTA) Performance Metrics
source.description: CDTA is a public transportation authority in the Capital Region.  This dataset presents information that reflects the organizations performance levels.  This dataset includes customer boarding’s, miles operated, accidents, preventative maintenance inspections, and complaints.
